song_lyrics: Hu joganiyā ho Shyām terī, Mohanlāl līje sudh merī... °ṭek
Tum kāran jogan hoy nikasī, lok kuṭumb lāj taj kerī;
Tere badan daras hit pyāre, nagar nagar deu nit ferī... Hu° 1
Shrī Ghanshyām lāḍīle Mohan, daras paras bhīkh nit derī;
Premānand ke Nāthajī terī, charan kamalkī hū mai cherī... Hu° 2
title: Hu joganiyā ho Shyām terī
